{
  "texts": [
    "We proposed \"XpertAI\", a framework leveraging XAI and LLMs to generate intelligent natural language explanations of structure-property relationships from raw chemistry data.",
    "In other words, XpertAI can be perceived as an LLM agent for hypotheses generation that consists of two main components: (1) XAI methods and (2) a RAG model.",
    "XpertAI produces readily interpretable and specific explanations while uncovering structure-property relationships.",
    "We showed integrating XAI and LLMs is more powerful than using either alone.",
    "Furthermore, we demonstrated that this combination can accurately explain input-output relationships, not just model predictions."
  ]
}